FT  18 JUL 94 / World News in Brief: Rolling settlement
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Rolling settlement for UK shares comes into force today. Under the new
system, shares must be delivered or paid for 10 business days after a
bargain is struck instead of the two or three weeks that has been
traditional on the London Stock Exchange.
